query:
DELETE t1 FROM task_completions t1
INNER JOIN task_completions t2 
WHERE t1.id < t2.id 
  AND t1.taskId = t2.taskId 
  AND t1.userId = t2.userId 
  AND DATE(t1.date) = DATE(t2.date)
